Breaking News
BREAKING: Buhari’s Chief Of Staff, Abba Kyari, Reportedly Sick, Suspected Of Contracting Coronavirus
0 Comments
3 Days Ago The online news medium went ahead on Tuesday to break the story of three of Kyari's staff contracting the virus from him. Till this moment, the Presidency has been unable to deny any of the reports, instead plotting to turn their anger on Sowore and SaharaReporters. 



